House GOP: Drop budget, focus on Afghanistan. Afghanistan is Benghazi on steroids. Rep. McCaul (R-Texas): Biden's "gonna have blood on his hands" over Afghanistan withdrawal. Biden is being bullied by the Taliban. On his last day as governor, Andrew Cuomo has International Emmy Award rescinded following sexual harassment scandal. Psaki's two big lies. Veteran caller pleads to help his Afghan translator trapped in Kabul. Will Louisiana fans get the shot to watch football?
